#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:11
msgid "Support Learnable Attention Sink"
msgstr "支持可学习 Attention Sink"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:13
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "引言"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:15
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Large-Scaled Models assign significant attention to few tokens (<em>such as "
"the intial tokens in the sequence</em>), even if they are not semantically "
"important, which is known as <b>attention sink</b> "
"{cite}`xiao2024efficientstreaminglanguagemodels`. Researchers attribute this"
" interesting phenomenon to the nature of {math}`softmax`, which requires "
"attention scores of each query token to always sum up to {math}`1` for all "
"key tokens in the context, even when some query token does not strongly "
"attend to any key token at all {cite}`gu2025attentionsinkemergeslanguage`. "
"Therefore, during the training, we can deliberately add some "
"<u><em>learnable sink tokens</em></u> to the key sequence for each query "
"token to collect those unneeded attention scores to relax the <em>\"sum-up-"
"to-one\"</em> constraint, as a learnable version of {math}`\\textit{off-by-"
"one}\\space softmax` {cite}`miller2025attentionmisc`."
msgstr ""
"大规模模型会将大量注意力分配给少数 token（<em>例如序列中的初始 token</em>），即使它们在语义上并不重要，这被称为 "
"<b>attention sink</b> "
"{cite}`xiao2024efficientstreaminglanguagemodels`。研究者将这一有趣现象归因于 "
"{math}`softmax` 的本质，它要求每个 query token 的注意力分数在上下文中所有 key token 上的总和始终为 "
"{math}`1`，即使某些 query token 根本不强烈关注任何 key token "
"{cite}`gu2025attentionsinkemergeslanguage`。因此，在训练过程中，我们可以有意地为每个 query token "
"在 key 序列中添加一些 <u><em>可学习的 sink token</em></u> 来收集那些不需要的注意力分数，以放松 "
"<em>\"总和为一\"</em> 的约束，作为 {math}`\\textit{off-by-one}\\space softmax` "
"{cite}`miller2025attentionmisc` 的可学习版本。"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:17
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"However, since sink tokens only affect the {math}`softmax` operation during "
"the attention forward/backward passes w.r.t. the GPT-OSS implementation "
"{cite}`openaiGPT-OSScode-misc`, <b>it is non-trivial to apply learnable "
"attention sink with the (distributed) attention implementations in the style"
" of <u>Flash Attention</u></b> "
"{cite}`dao2022flashattention_attn_sink,dao2023flashattention_attn_sink,shah2024flashattention3fastaccurateattention_attn_sink`,"
" particularly our own kernel implemenation of <u>Flex-Flash-Attention</u>, "
"as well as the distributed implementation of <u>MagiAttention</u> "
"{cite}`magiattention2025_attn_sink`."
msgstr ""
"然而，由于 sink token 仅影响 GPT-OSS 实现 {cite}`openaiGPT-OSScode-misc` "
"中注意力前向/反向传播期间的 {math}`softmax` 操作，<b>在 <u>Flash Attention</u> "
"风格的（分布式）注意力实现中应用可学习 attention sink 并非易事</b> "
"{cite}`dao2022flashattention_attn_sink,dao2023flashattention_attn_sink,shah2024flashattention3fastaccurateattention_attn_sink`，特别是我们自己的"
" <u>Flex-Flash-Attention</u> 内核实现，以及 <u>MagiAttention</u> "
"{cite}`magiattention2025_attn_sink` 的分布式实现。"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:20
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "概览"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:22
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"With the release of [MagiAttention-v1.0.5](https://github.com/SandAI-"
"org/MagiAttention/releases/tag/v1.0.5), we have not only <b>supported the "
"learnable attention sink mechanism</b> for our own kernel / distributed "
"implementations of <u>Flex-Flash-Attention</u> / <u>MagiAttention</u> "
"respectively, but also <b>provided the <em>plug-and-play</em> "
"implementations</b> to integrate the original <u>Flash Attention</u> 2/3 "
"interface {cite}`daoFlashAttnInterfaceMisc,daoFlashAttnInterfaceHopperMisc` "
"with attention sink, as one of the [MagiAttention "
"Extensions](https://github.com/SandAI-"
"org/MagiAttention/tree/main/extensions#flashattention-with-attention-sink-)."
msgstr ""
"随着 [MagiAttention-v1.0.5](https://github.com/SandAI-"
"org/MagiAttention/releases/tag/v1.0.5) 的发布，我们不仅分别为自己的 <u>Flex-Flash-"
"Attention</u> / <u>MagiAttention</u> 内核/分布式实现 <b>支持了可学习 attention sink "
"机制</b>，还 <b>提供了<em>即插即用</em>的实现</b>，将原始 <u>Flash Attention</u> 2/3 接口 "
"{cite}`daoFlashAttnInterfaceMisc,daoFlashAttnInterfaceHopperMisc` 与 "
"attention sink 集成，作为 [MagiAttention 扩展](https://github.com/SandAI-"
"org/MagiAttention/tree/main/extensions#flashattention-with-attention-sink-) "
"之一。"

