#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:32
msgid "User Interface"
msgstr "用户接口"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:34
msgid ""
"Below, we show the minor update of the user interfaces to support learnable "
"attention sink mechanism for original Flex-Flash-Attention, MagiAttention, "
"as well as the Flash-Attention 2/3 as one of the [MagiAttention "
"Extensions](https://github.com/SandAI-"
"org/MagiAttention/tree/main/extensions#flashattention-with-attention-sink-)."
msgstr ""
"下面，我们展示了为支持可学习 attention sink 机制而对原始 Flex-Flash-Attention、MagiAttention 以及作为"
" [MagiAttention 扩展](https://github.com/SandAI-"
"org/MagiAttention/tree/main/extensions#flashattention-with-attention-sink-) "
"之一的 Flash-Attention 2/3 用户接口的少量更新。"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:37
msgid "FFA API"
msgstr "FFA API"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:39
msgid ""
"Just add an optional tensor `sink` to the argument list of "
"`flex_flash_attn_func`."
msgstr "只需在 `flex_flash_attn_func` 的参数列表中添加一个可选张量 `sink`。"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:40
msgid ""
"And when and only when `sink` tensor is given, `flex_flash_attn_func` will "
"apply attention sink during the forward pass, and compute `dsink`  (<em>the "
"gradient of `sink`</em>) during the backward pass."
msgstr ""
"当且仅当给定 `sink` 张量时，`flex_flash_attn_func` 将在前向传播中应用 attention sink，并在反向传播中计算 "
"`dsink`（<em>`sink` 的梯度</em>）。"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:41 ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:70
#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:95
msgid ""
"Otherwise, attention sink is skipped and `dsink` is also returned as `None`."
msgstr "否则，attention sink 将被跳过，`dsink` 也将返回 `None`。"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:42 ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:71
#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:96
msgid "dtype: `float32` only."
msgstr "数据类型：仅 `float32`。"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:43 ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:72
msgid "shape: `[seqlen_sink, num_heads_q]`, where `seqlen_sink` in `[1, 8]`."
msgstr "形状：`[seqlen_sink, num_heads_q]`，其中 `seqlen_sink` 在 `[1, 8]` 范围内。"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:44
msgid "interface difference with the original `flex_flash_attn_func`:"
msgstr "与原始 `flex_flash_attn_func` 的接口差异："

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:65
msgid "MagiAttn API"
msgstr "MagiAttn API"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:67
msgid ""
"Just add an optional **replicated** tensor `sink` to the argument list of "
"`calc_attn`."
msgstr "只需在 `calc_attn` 的参数列表中添加一个可选的**复制**张量 `sink`。"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:68
msgid ""
"And when and only when **replicated** `sink` tensor is given, `calc_attn` "
"will apply attention sink during the forward pass for each **local** query "
"token, and compute **partial** `dsink` during the backward pass."
msgstr ""
"当且仅当给定**复制的** `sink` 张量时，`calc_attn` 将在前向传播中为每个**本地** query token 应用 "
"attention sink，并在反向传播中计算**部分** `dsink`。"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:69
msgid ""
"And an `all-reduce` communication might be applied across cp ranks to return"
" the **reduced** `dsink` if required (<em>see the environment variable "
"`MAGI_ATTENTION_DSINK_ALL_REDUCE_OP` in our [docs](https://sandai-"
"org.github.io/MagiAttention/docs/main/env_variables.html#for-"
"correctness)</em>)."
msgstr ""
"如果需要，可能会跨 cp rank 应用 `all-reduce` 通信以返回**归约后的** `dsink`（<em>参见我们 "
"[文档](https://sandai-"
"org.github.io/MagiAttention/docs/main/env_variables.html#for-correctness) "
"中的环境变量 `MAGI_ATTENTION_DSINK_ALL_REDUCE_OP`</em>）。"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:73
msgid "parallel style: `Replicate`."
msgstr "并行方式：`Replicate`。"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:74
msgid "interface difference with the original `calc_attn`:"
msgstr "与原始 `calc_attn` 的接口差异："

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:91
msgid "Flash Attention Extension"
msgstr "Flash Attention 扩展"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:93
msgid ""
"Just add an optional tensor `sink` to the argument list of "
"`flash_attn_func`, `flash_attn_varlen_func`, etc."
msgstr ""
"只需在 `flash_attn_func`、`flash_attn_varlen_func` 等的参数列表中添加一个可选张量 `sink`。"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:94
msgid ""
"And when and only when `sink` tensor is given, flash attention will apply "
"attention sink during the forward pass, and compute `dsink` during the "
"backward pass."
msgstr ""
"当且仅当给定 `sink` 张量时，Flash Attention 将在前向传播中应用 attention sink，并在反向传播中计算 "
"`dsink`。"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:97
msgid "shape: `[seqlen_sink, num_heads_q]`, where `seqlen_sink` has no limit."
msgstr "形状：`[seqlen_sink, num_heads_q]`，其中 `seqlen_sink` 没有限制。"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:98
msgid "interface difference with the original flash attention:"
msgstr "与原始 Flash Attention 的接口差异："

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:133
msgid "Math Derivation"
msgstr "数学推导"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:135
msgid ""
"Below, we provide the step-by-step math derivation of the original forward /"
" backward passes for Flex-Flash-Attention (<em>the same as Flash-"
"Attention</em>) w/o sink tokens, and then the differences when involving the"
" learnable attention sink mechanism, serving as the guidence for our "
"implementations in the next section."
msgstr ""
"下面，我们提供原始 Flex-Flash-Attention（<em>与 Flash-Attention 相同</em>）无 sink token "
"的前向/反向传播的逐步数学推导，以及涉及可学习 attention sink 机制时的差异，作为下一节实现的指导。"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:138
msgid ""
"To simplify the derivation, we drop the `batch` dimension and only keep the "
"`num_heads` dimension to the leftmost acting as the implicit `batch` "
"dimension."
msgstr "为简化推导，我们省略 `batch` 维度，仅保留最左侧的 `num_heads` 维度作为隐式 `batch` 维度。"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:140
msgid ""
"To focus on the attention sink mechanism, we assume you're already familiar "
"with Flash Attention and will skip over its finer details, like the "
"<em>double-loop tiling</em> strategy and the derivation of <em>online "
"softmax correction</em> based on `log-sum-exp` operations."
msgstr ""
"为了聚焦于 attention sink 机制，我们假设您已经熟悉 Flash "
"Attention，并将跳过其更细节的部分，如<em>双循环分块</em>策略和基于 `log-sum-exp` 操作的<em>在线 softmax "
"校正</em>推导。"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:142
msgid ""
"If you are new to Flash Attention or well-interested in the full original "
"math derivation, <b>we highly recommend our another blog post: [Flash "
"Attention 2 Math Derivation](./fa2_math_derivation.md)</b>."
msgstr ""
"如果您是 Flash Attention 新手或对完整的原始数学推导很感兴趣，<b>我们强烈推荐我们的另一篇博客文章：[Flash Attention "
"2 数学推导](./fa2_math_derivation.md)</b>。"

