#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:158
msgid "FFA Forward"
msgstr "FFA 前向"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:160
msgid "FFA forward w/o sink tokens"
msgstr "FFA 前向（无 sink token）"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:162
msgid "step1:"
msgstr "步骤1："

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:164
msgid ""
"\\begin{aligned}\n"
"S &= Q K^{\\mathrm{T}} \\cdot \\mathrm{scale} + \\mathrm{bias} \\\\\n"
"\\text{where } & Q \\in \\mathbb{R}^{n_{hq} \\times s_q \\times h_d},\\; K \\in \\mathbb{R}^{n_{hk} \\times s_k \\times h_d}, \\\\\n"
"& \\mathrm{scale} \\in \\mathbb{R},\\; \\mathrm{bias} \\in \\mathbb{R}^{n_{hq} \\times s_q \\times s_k},\\; S \\in \\mathbb{R}^{n_{hq} \\times s_q \\times s_k}\n"
"\\end{aligned}"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:174 ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:207
msgid "step2:"
msgstr "步骤2："

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:176
msgid ""
"\\begin{aligned}\n"
"\\mathrm{softmax}_{\\mathrm{row}}(X_i) &= \\frac{\\exp(X_i - M_i)}{L_i}, \\quad i \\in [1, s_q] \\\\\n"
"\\text{where } M_i &= \\mathrm{rowmax}(X_i), \\quad L_i = \\mathrm{rowsum}(\\exp(X_i - M_i))\n"
"\\end{aligned}"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:184
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"\\begin{aligned}\n"
"&P = \\mathrm{softmax}_{row}(S) \\notag \\\\\n"
"&where\\; S, P \\in \\mathbb{R}^{nhq\\times sq\\times sk} \\notag\n"
"\\end{aligned}"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:191 ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:226
#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:283 ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:353
msgid "step3:"
msgstr "步骤3："

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:193
msgid ""
"\\begin{aligned}\n"
"O &= P \\times V, \\quad \\mathrm{LSE}_i = \\log(L_i) + M_i, \\quad i \\in [1, s_q] \\\\\n"
"\\text{where } & P \\in \\mathbb{R}^{n_{hq} \\times s_q \\times s_k}, \\quad V \\in \\mathbb{R}^{n_{hk} \\times s_k \\times h_d}, \\\\\n"
"& O \\in \\mathbb{R}^{n_{hq} \\times s_q \\times h_d}, \\quad \\mathrm{LSE} \\in \\mathbb{R}^{n_{hq} \\times s_q}\n"
"\\end{aligned}"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:203
msgid "FFA forward with sink tokens"
msgstr "FFA 前向（有 sink token）"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:205
#, python-brace-format
msgid "step1: <em>the same with {eq}`ffa_forward_wo_sink_step1`</em>"
msgstr "步骤1：<em>与 {eq}`ffa_forward_wo_sink_step1` 相同</em>"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:209
msgid ""
"\\begin{aligned}\n"
"\\tilde{P} &= \\mathrm{softmax}_{\\mathrm{row}}(\\tilde{S}), \\quad \\tilde{S}_i = [S_i, \\mathrm{sink}], \\quad i \\in [1, s_q] \\\\\n"
"\\text{where } & \\tilde{S}, \\tilde{P} \\in \\mathbb{R}^{n_{hq} \\times s_q \\times (s_k + s_{\\mathrm{sink}})}, \\quad \\mathrm{sink} \\in \\mathbb{R}^{n_{hq} \\times s_{\\mathrm{sink}}}\n"
"\\end{aligned}"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:218
msgid ""
"\\begin{aligned}\n"
"\\tilde{P}_i &= [\\tilde{P}^{\\mathrm{qk}}_{i}, P^{\\mathrm{sink}}_{i}], \\quad i \\in [1, s_q] \\\\\n"
"\\text{where } & \\tilde{P}^{\\mathrm{qk}} \\in \\mathbb{R}^{n_{hq} \\times s_q \\times s_k}, \\\\\n"
"& P^{\\mathrm{sink}} \\in \\mathbb{R}^{n_{hq} \\times s_q \\times s_{\\mathrm{sink}}}\n"
"\\end{aligned}"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:228
msgid ""
"\\begin{aligned}\n"
"&\\tilde{O} = \\tilde{P}^{qk} \\times V, \\;\\tilde{\\mathrm{LSE}}_i = \\log(\\tilde{L}_i) + M_i, \\; i \\in [1, sq] \\\\\n"
"&\\tilde{L}_i = L_i + \\sum\\limits_{j=1}^{s_{\\mathrm{sink}}}\\mathrm{exp}(sink_j - M_i), \\; i \\in [1, sq] \\\\\n"
"&\\tilde{P}^{qk}_i = P^{qk}_i \\times \\cfrac{L_i}{\\tilde{L}_i}, \\; i \\in [1, sq] \\\\\n"
"&\\text{where } P^{qk},\\tilde{P}^{qk} \\in \\mathbb{R}^{nhq\\times sq\\times sk}, \\; V \\in \\mathbb{R}^{nhk\\times sk\\times hd}, \\\\\n"
"&\\tilde{O} \\in \\mathbb{R}^{nhq\\times sq\\times hd}, \\;\\tilde{\\mathrm{LSE}} \\in \\mathbb{R}^{nhq\\times sq}\n"
"\\end{aligned}"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:239
msgid ""
"<b>sink correction</b>: <em>as a post-processing of original ffa forward w/o"
" sink tokens</em>"
msgstr "<b>sink 校正</b>：<em>作为原始 FFA 前向（无 sink token）的后处理</em>"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:241
msgid ""
"\\begin{aligned}\n"
"&\\mathrm{LSE}^{sink} = \\log\\big(\\sum\\limits_{j=1}^{s_{\\mathrm{sink}}}\\mathrm{exp}(sink_j)\\big) \\\\\n"
"&\\tilde{\\mathrm{LSE}}_i = \\log\\big(\\exp(\\mathrm{LSE}_i) + \\exp(\\mathrm{LSE}^{sink})\\big), \\; i \\in [1, sq] \\\\\n"
"&\\tilde{O} = O \\cdot \\exp\\big(\\mathrm{LSE} - \\tilde{\\mathrm{LSE}}\\big) \\\\\n"
"&\\text{where } sink \\in \\mathbb{R}^{nhq\\times s_{\\mathrm{sink}}},\\;\\mathrm{LSE}^{sink} \\in \\mathbb{R}^{nhq} \\\\\n"
"&\\mathrm{LSE},\\tilde{\\mathrm{LSE}} \\in \\mathbb{R}^{nhq\\times sq}, \\;O,\\tilde{O}\\in \\mathbb{R}^{nhq\\times sq\\times hd}\n"
"\\end{aligned}"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:252
msgid "FFA Backward"
msgstr "FFA 反向"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:254
msgid "FFA backward w/o sink tokens"
msgstr "FFA 反向（无 sink token）"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:256
msgid "step1: <em>as a pre-processing</em>"
msgstr "步骤1：<em>作为预处理</em>"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:258
msgid ""
"\\begin{aligned}\n"
"&\\Delta_i = P^{\\mathrm T}_i \\times dP_i = O^{\\mathrm T}_i \\times dO_i,\\quad i \\in [1, s_q] \\\\[4pt]\n"
"&\\Delta = \\mathrm{sum}_{hd}(O \\;\\odot\\; dO)\n"
"\\\\[4pt]\n"
"&\\text{where } O,dO \\in \\mathbb{R}^{n_{hq}\\times s_q\\times h_d},\\; \\Delta \\in \\mathbb{R}^{n_{hq}\\times s_q}\n"
"\\end{aligned}"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:269 ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:339
msgid "step2: <em>recomputation</em>"
msgstr "步骤2：<em>重计算</em>"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:271
msgid ""
"\\begin{aligned}\n"
"&S = Q \\times K^{\\mathrm T} \\cdot \\mathrm{scale} \\; + \\; \\mathrm{bias} \\\\[4pt]\n"
"&P_i = \\exp\\big(S_i - \\mathrm{LSE}_i\\big), \\quad i \\in [1, s_q] \\\\[4pt]\n"
"&\\text{where } Q \\in \\mathbb{R}^{n_{hq}\\times s_q\\times h_d},\\; K \\in \\mathbb{R}^{n_{hk}\\times s_k\\times h_d}, \\\\[2pt]\n"
"&\\mathrm{scale} \\in \\mathbb{R},\\; \\mathrm{bias} \\in \\mathbb{R}^{n_{hq}\\times s_q\\times s_k}, \\\\[2pt]\n"
"&S,P \\in \\mathbb{R}^{n_{hq}\\times s_q\\times s_k},\\; \\mathrm{LSE} \\in \\mathbb{R}^{n_{hq}\\times s_q}\n"
"\\end{aligned}"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:285
msgid ""
"\\begin{aligned}\n"
"&dV = P^{\\mathrm T} \\times dO \\\\[4pt]\n"
"&dP = dO \\times V^{\\mathrm T} \\\\[4pt]\n"
"&\\text{where } P,dP \\in \\mathbb{R}^{n_{hq}\\times s_q\\times s_k},\\; V,dV \\in \\mathbb{R}^{n_{hk}\\times s_k\\times h_d},\\\\[2pt]\n"
"&dO \\in \\mathbb{R}^{n_{hq}\\times s_q\\times h_d}\n"
"\\end{aligned}"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:296 ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:365
msgid "step4:"
msgstr "步骤4："

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:298
msgid ""
"\\begin{aligned}\n"
"&dS_i = P_i \\odot (dP_i - \\Delta_i), \\quad i \\in [1, s_q] \\\\[4pt]\n"
"&\\text{where } P,dP \\in \\mathbb{R}^{n_{hq}\\times s_q\\times s_k},\\; dS \\in \\mathbb{R}^{n_{hq}\\times s_q\\times s_k},\\\\[2pt]\n"
"&\\Delta \\in \\mathbb{R}^{n_{hq}\\times s_q}\n"
"\\end{aligned}"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:308
msgid "step5:"
msgstr "步骤5："

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:310
msgid ""
"\\begin{aligned}\n"
"&\\hat{dS} = dS \\cdot \\mathrm{scale} \\\\[4pt]\n"
"&dQ = \\hat{dS} \\times K \\\\[4pt]\n"
"&dK = \\hat{dS}^{\\mathrm T} \\times Q \\\\[4pt]\n"
"&\\text{where } dS,\\hat{dS} \\in \\mathbb{R}^{n_{hq}\\times s_q\\times s_k},\\; \\mathrm{scale}\\in\\mathbb{R},\\\\[2pt]\n"
"&Q,dQ \\in \\mathbb{R}^{n_{hq}\\times s_q\\times h_d},\\; K,dK \\in \\mathbb{R}^{n_{hk}\\times s_k\\times h_d}\n"
"\\end{aligned}"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:323
msgid "FFA backward with sink tokens"
msgstr "FFA 反向（有 sink token）"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:325
msgid "step1: <em>as a pre-processing as well</em>"
msgstr "步骤1：<em>同样作为预处理</em>"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:327
msgid ""
"\\begin{aligned}\n"
"&\\tilde{\\Delta}_i = \\tilde{P}_i^{\\mathrm T} \\times dP_i = [\\tilde{P}^{qk}_i, P^{sink}_i]^{\\mathrm T} \\times [dP^{qk}_i, dP^{sink}_i] \\\\\n"
"&\\quad\\;=\\; {\\tilde{P}^{qk}_i}^{\\mathrm T} \\times dP^{qk}_i \\;+\\; {P^{sink}_i}^{\\mathrm T} \\times dP^{sink}_i \\\\\n"
"&\\quad\\;=\\; {\\tilde{P}^{qk}_i}^{\\mathrm T} \\times dP^{qk}_i \\;=\\; \\tilde{O}_i^{\\mathrm T} \\times dO_i,\\quad i\\in[1,s_q] \\\\\n"
"&\\tilde{\\Delta} = \\mathrm{sum}_{hd}(\\tilde{O}\\odot dO) \\\\\n"
"&\\text{where }\\tilde{O},dO\\in\\mathbb{R}^{n_{hq}\\times s_q\\times h_d},\\; \\tilde{\\Delta}\\in\\mathbb{R}^{n_{hq}\\times s_q}\n"
"\\end{aligned}"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:341
msgid ""
"\\begin{aligned}\n"
"&S = QK^{\\mathrm T}\\cdot\\mathrm{scale} + \\mathrm{bias} \\\\\n"
"&\\tilde{S}_i = [S_i,\\,\\mathrm{sink}],\\quad i\\in[1,s_q] \\\\\n"
"&\\tilde{P}_i = \\exp\\big(\\tilde{S}_i - \\tilde{\\mathrm{LSE}}_i\\big),\\quad i\\in[1,s_q] \\\\\n"
"&\\tilde{P}_i = [\\tilde{P}^{qk}_i,\\,P^{sink}_i] \\\\\n"
"&\\text{where } \\tilde{S},\\tilde{P}\\in\\mathbb{R}^{n_{hq}\\times s_q\\times (s_k+s_{\\mathrm{sink}})},\\; \\tilde{\\mathrm{LSE}}\\in\\mathbb{R}^{n_{hq}\\times s_q}\n"
"\\end{aligned}"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:355
msgid ""
"\\begin{aligned}\n"
"&dV = {\\tilde{P}}^{\\mathrm T}\\times dO \\\\\n"
"&dP = dO\\times V^{\\mathrm T} \\\\\n"
"&\\text{where } \\tilde{P},dP\\in\\mathbb{R}^{n_{hq}\\times s_q\\times (s_k+s_{\\mathrm{sink}})},\\; dV\\in\\mathbb{R}^{n_{hk}\\times s_k\\times h_d}\n"
"\\end{aligned}"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:367
msgid ""
"\\begin{aligned}\n"
"&\\tilde{dS}_i = \\tilde{P}_i \\odot (dP_i - \\tilde{\\Delta}_i) = [dS_i,\\,dsink_i],\\quad i\\in[1,s_q] \\\\\n"
"&dS_i = \\tilde{P}^{qk}_i \\odot (dP^{qk}_i - \\tilde{\\Delta}_i) \\\\\n"
"&dsink_i = P^{sink}_i \\odot (dP^{sink}_i - \\tilde{\\Delta}_i) = -\\,P^{sink}_i\\odot\\tilde{\\Delta}_i \\quad(\\text{since } dP^{sink}_i=0)\\\\\n"
"&dsink = \\sum_{i=1}^{s_q} dsink_i = {P^{sink}}^{\\mathrm T}\\times(-\\tilde{\\Delta}) \\\\\n"
"&\\text{where } dS\\in\\mathbb{R}^{n_{hq}\\times s_q\\times s_k},\\; dsink\\in\\mathbb{R}^{n_{hq}\\times s_{\\mathrm{sink}}}\n"
"\\end{aligned}"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:379
#, python-brace-format
msgid "step5: <em>the same with {eq}`ffa_backward_wo_sink_step5`</em>"
msgstr "步骤5：<em>与 {eq}`ffa_backward_wo_sink_step5` 相同</em>"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:381
msgid ""
"dsink computation: <em>as another pre-processing of original ffa backward "
"w/o sink tokens</em>"
msgstr "dsink 计算：<em>作为原始 FFA 反向（无 sink token）的另一个预处理</em>"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:383
msgid ""
"\\begin{aligned}\n"
"&dsink = {P^{sink}}^{\\mathrm T}\\times(-\\tilde{\\Delta})\n"
"= -\\sum_{i=1}^{s_q}\\big(\\exp(\\mathrm{sink}-\\tilde{\\mathrm{LSE}}_i)\\cdot\\tilde{\\Delta}_i\\big) \\\\\n"
"&\\text{where } \\mathrm{sink},dsink\\in\\mathbb{R}^{n_{hq}\\times s_{\\mathrm{sink}}},\\; \\tilde{\\mathrm{LSE}},\\tilde{\\Delta}\\in\\mathbb{R}^{n_{hq}\\times s_q}\n"
"\\end{aligned}"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:394
msgid "Implementations"
msgstr "实现"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:396
msgid ""
"Based on the math derivation in the previous section, folding a learnable "
"attention sink into the attention implementations in the Flash Attention "
"style boils down to just two edits:"
msgstr "基于上一节的数学推导，将可学习 attention sink 融入 Flash Attention 风格的注意力实现归结为两处修改："

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:398
msgid ""
"For forward pass, we have nothing to change about the original "
"implementation, but should apply an additional post-processing to correct "
"the returned `out` and `lse` with `sink` tokens (<em>see the <b>sink "
"correction</b> of the [FFA forward with sink tokens](#ffa-forward-with-sink-"
"tokens)</em>)."
msgstr ""
"对于前向传播，我们无需更改原始实现，但应应用额外的后处理来用 `sink` token 校正返回的 `out` 和 `lse`（<em>参见[带 "
"sink token 的 FFA 前向](#ffa-forward-with-sink-tokens)的 <b>sink 校正</b></em>）。"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:399
msgid ""
"For backward pass, we have nothing to change about the original "
"implementation, but should apply an additional pre-processing to compute the"
" `dsink`, i.e. the gradient of `sink` (<em>see the <b>dsink computation</b> "
"of the [FFA backward with sink tokens](#ffa-backward-with-sink-"
"tokens)</em>)."
msgstr ""
"对于反向传播，我们无需更改原始实现，但应应用额外的预处理来计算 `dsink`，即 `sink` 的梯度（<em>参见[带 sink token 的 "
"FFA 反向](#ffa-backward-with-sink-tokens)的 <b>dsink 计算</b></em>）。"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:401
msgid ""
"Therefore, we share the following code snippets to present our "
"implementations of the learnable attention sink mechanism: a naive PyTorch "
"reference, Flex-Flash-Attention (<em>both internal and external to the "
"kernels, which fit Flash Attention as well</em>), and the distributed "
"implementation of MagiAttention."
msgstr ""
"因此，我们分享以下代码片段来展示我们的可学习 attention sink 机制实现：一个简单的 PyTorch 参考实现、Flex-Flash-"
"Attention（<em>内核内部和外部实现，同样适用于 Flash Attention</em>），以及 MagiAttention 的分布式实现。"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:404
msgid "Torch Reference"
msgstr "Torch 参考实现"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:406
msgid "reference implementation w/o sink tokens:"
msgstr "无 sink token 的参考实现："

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:428
msgid "reference implementation difference with sink tokens:"
msgstr "有 sink token 的参考实现差异："

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:459
msgid "FFA Impl"
msgstr "FFA 实现"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:461
msgid "FFA Forward Impl"
msgstr "FFA 前向实现"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:463 ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:500
msgid "External Impl"
msgstr "外部实现"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:465
msgid ""
"Use <b>sink correction</b> to correct `out`, `lse` after the ffa forward "
"kernel returns, as an external post-processing kernel (<em>which is the way "
"we extend the Flash Attention 2/3 forward with sink tokens, and see the "
"[source code](https://github.com/SandAI-"
"org/MagiAttention/blob/main/extensions/magi_attn_extensions/fa3_interface_with_sink.py)"
" for more detals</em>):"
msgstr ""
"使用 <b>sink 校正</b> 在 FFA 前向内核返回后校正 `out`、`lse`，作为外部后处理内核（<em>这是我们用 sink token"
" 扩展 Flash Attention 2/3 前向的方式，详情请参阅[源代码](https://github.com/SandAI-"
"org/MagiAttention/blob/main/extensions/magi_attn_extensions/fa3_interface_with_sink.py)</em>）："

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:483 ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:526
msgid "Internal Impl"
msgstr "内部实现"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:485
msgid ""
"Since FFA forward already has a post-processing kernel "
"`FlashAttnFwdPostprocess` to zero-fill up the never-stored rows of `O`, "
"indicated by \"whether the corr. row of `lse` is still `-inf`\", ..."
msgstr ""
"由于 FFA 前向已经有一个后处理内核 `FlashAttnFwdPostprocess`，用于零填充从未存储的 `O` 行，通过“对应的 `lse` "
"行是否仍为 `-inf`”来判断……"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:487
msgid ""
"Then we can fuse the <b>sink correction</b> process into the "
"`FlashAttnFwdPostprocess` kernel as follows (<em>see the [source "
"code](https://github.com/SandAI-"
"org/MagiAttention/blob/main/magi_attention/csrc/flexible_flash_attention/flash_fwd_postprocess_kernel.h)"
" for more details</em>):"
msgstr ""
"然后我们可以将 <b>sink 校正</b> 过程融合到 `FlashAttnFwdPostprocess` "
"内核中，如下所示（<em>详情请参阅[源代码](https://github.com/SandAI-"
"org/MagiAttention/blob/main/magi_attention/csrc/flexible_flash_attention/flash_fwd_postprocess_kernel.h)</em>）："

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:489
msgid "As for lse correction:"
msgstr "关于 lse 校正："

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:490
msgid ""
"If the current row of `lse` is not `-inf`, then we update this row of `lse` "
"with `lse_sink`."
msgstr "如果当前行的 `lse` 不是 `-inf`，则用 `lse_sink` 更新该行的 `lse`。"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:491
msgid ""
"Otherwise, the `lse` should also be filled up with `lse_sink`, instead of "
"`-inf`."
msgstr "否则，`lse` 也应该用 `lse_sink` 填充，而不是 `-inf`。"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:493
msgid "As for out correction:"
msgstr "关于 out 校正："

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:494
msgid ""
"If the current row of `lse` is not `-inf`, then load the corr. row of `O`, "
"rescale it and write it back."
msgstr "如果当前行的 `lse` 不是 `-inf`，则加载对应行的 `O`，重新缩放并写回。"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:495
msgid ""
"Otherwise, the corr. row of `O` still needs to be filled up with `0`, so the"
" same as before."
msgstr "否则，对应行的 `O` 仍需用 `0` 填充，与之前相同。"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:498
msgid "FFA Backward Impl"
msgstr "FFA 反向实现"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:502
msgid ""
"Use <b>dsink computation</b> to compute dsink before the ffa backward kernel"
" launchs, as an external pre-processing kernel (<em>which is the way we "
"extend the Flash Attention 2/3 backward with sink tokens, and see the "
"[source code](https://github.com/SandAI-"
"org/MagiAttention/blob/main/extensions/magi_attn_extensions/fa3_interface_with_sink.py)"
" for more detals</em>):"
msgstr ""
"使用 <b>dsink 计算</b> 在 FFA 反向内核启动前计算 dsink，作为外部预处理内核（<em>这是我们用 sink token 扩展 "
"Flash Attention 2/3 反向的方式，详情请参阅[源代码](https://github.com/SandAI-"
"org/MagiAttention/blob/main/extensions/magi_attn_extensions/fa3_interface_with_sink.py)</em>）："

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:528
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Since FFA backward already has a pre-processing kernel "
"`FlashAttnBwdPreprocess` to compute {math}`\\Delta` (<em>in FA / FFA, we "
"name it `dPsum`</em>), w.r.t. the step1 in the [FFA backward w/o sink "
"tokens](#ffa-backward-wo-sink-tokens), ..."
msgstr ""
"由于 FFA 反向已经有一个预处理内核 `FlashAttnBwdPreprocess` 来计算 {math}`\\Delta`（<em>在 FA / "
"FFA 中，我们将其命名为 `dPsum`</em>），对应 [FFA 反向（无 sink token）](#ffa-backward-wo-sink-"
"tokens) 中的步骤1……"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:530
msgid ""
"The we can fuse the <b>dsink computation</b> process into the "
"`FlashAttnBwdPreprocess` kernel as follows (<em>see the [source "
"code](https://github.com/SandAI-"
"org/MagiAttention/blob/main/magi_attention/csrc/flexible_flash_attention/flash_bwd_preprocess_kernel.h)"
" for more details</em>):"
msgstr ""
"然后我们可以将 <b>dsink 计算</b> 过程融合到 `FlashAttnBwdPreprocess` "
"内核中，如下所示（<em>详情请参阅[源代码](https://github.com/SandAI-"
"org/MagiAttention/blob/main/magi_attention/csrc/flexible_flash_attention/flash_bwd_preprocess_kernel.h)</em>）："

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:532
msgid ""
"As for `lse`, the same as before, each thread in one block loads one unique "
"row of `lse`."
msgstr "关于 `lse`，与之前相同，一个 block 中的每个线程加载一个唯一行的 `lse`。"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:534
msgid ""
"As for `p_sink`, the first `seqlen_sink` of threads in one block load the "
"`sink` to shared memory, and each thread computes `p_sink = exp(sink - lse)`"
" with its own unique row of `lse`, storing to shared memory as well."
msgstr ""
"关于 `p_sink`，一个 block 中的前 `seqlen_sink` 个线程将 `sink` 加载到共享内存，每个线程使用自己唯一行的 "
"`lse` 计算 `p_sink = exp(sink - lse)`，同样存储到共享内存。"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:536
msgid ""
"As for `dPsum`, the same as before, each block loads a unique `kBlockM` rows"
" of `O` and `dO`, applies `O * dO`, reduces across the head dimension to get"
" the local block of `dPsum` in register files, and stores it to global "
"memory."
msgstr ""
"关于 `dPsum`，与之前相同，每个 block 加载唯一的 `kBlockM` 行 `O` 和 `dO`，执行 `O * "
"dO`，在头维度上归约以在寄存器文件中获得 `dPsum` 的本地块，然后存储到全局内存。"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:538
msgid ""
"As for `d_sink`, since it requires to be reduced across the whole `seqlen_q`"
" dimension, the following steps are performed:"
msgstr "关于 `d_sink`，由于需要在整个 `seqlen_q` 维度上归约，执行以下步骤："

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:539
msgid ""
"step1: each thread loads a unique row of `dPsum` from register files and the"
" corr. row of `p_sink` from shared memory, and computes thread-partial "
"`dsink = p_sink * -dPsum` for this row, and stores to  shared memory first "
"(<em>since `p_sink` is not used afterwards, we can reuse its shared memory "
"buffer to store `dsink`</em>)."
msgstr ""
"步骤1：每个线程从寄存器文件加载唯一行的 `dPsum` 和从共享内存加载对应行的 `p_sink`，计算该行的线程级部分 `dsink = "
"p_sink * -dPsum`，先存储到共享内存（<em>由于之后不再使用 `p_sink`，我们可以复用其共享内存缓冲区来存储 "
"`dsink`</em>）。"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:540
msgid ""
"step2: each block loads all the thread-partial `dsink` from shared memory, "
"applies a `block-reduction` to get the block-reduced `dsink` for these "
"`kBlockM` rows, and stores it to a temporary buffer in global memory."
msgstr ""
"步骤2：每个 block 从共享内存加载所有线程级部分 `dsink`，执行 `block-reduction` 以获得这些 `kBlockM` 行的 "
"block 级归约 `dsink`，并存储到全局内存中的临时缓冲区。"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:541
msgid ""
"step3: after a device-level memory fence, the last block who stores its "
"block-reduced `dsink` loads all the block-reduced `dsink` back from the "
"temporary buffer, applies another `block-reduction` to get the reduced "
"`dsink` across the whole `seqlen_q` dimension, and finally stores it to "
"global memory."
msgstr ""
"步骤3：在设备级内存屏障之后，最后一个存储其 block 级归约 `dsink` 的 block 从临时缓冲区加载回所有 block 级归约的 "
"`dsink`，执行另一次 `block-reduction` 以获得跨整个 `seqlen_q` 维度的归约 `dsink`，最终存储到全局内存。"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:544
msgid "MagiAttn Impl"
msgstr "MagiAttn 实现"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:546
msgid "MagiAttn Forward"
msgstr "MagiAttn 前向"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:548
msgid ""
"Since `sink` is replicated across cp ranks, we can easily apply attention "
"sink by just passing `sink` into `_flex_flash_attn_forward`."
msgstr ""
"由于 `sink` 在 cp rank 间复制，我们可以简单地将 `sink` 传入 `_flex_flash_attn_forward` 来轻松应用 "
"attention sink。"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:549
msgid ""
"However, the attention sink is supposed to be applied <u>once and only "
"once</u> for the same query token, thus we can apply it at the host stage, "
"i.e. each cp rank only applies to their own local `q`."
msgstr ""
"然而，attention sink 应该对同一个 query token <u>有且仅有一次</u>应用，因此我们可以在 host 阶段应用它，即每个 "
"cp rank 仅对其本地 `q` 应用。"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:550
msgid ""
"Then, If the host stage is not skipped, just apply attention sink by passing"
" `sink` into `_flex_flash_attn_forward`:"
msgstr ""
"然后，如果 host 阶段未被跳过，只需将 `sink` 传入 `_flex_flash_attn_forward` 来应用 attention "
"sink："

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:567
msgid ""
"Otherwise, we should zero-initialize `local_out` as before, but initialize "
"`local_lse` with `lse_sink`, instead of `-inf`"
msgstr "否则，我们应像之前一样零初始化 `local_out`，但用 `lse_sink` 初始化 `local_lse`，而不是 `-inf`"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:594
msgid "MagiAttn Backward"
msgstr "MagiAttn 反向"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:596
msgid ""
"The same to the forward, to form a complete, non-overlapping breakdown of "
"`dsink` computation, we can compute partial `dsink` by just passing `sink` "
"into `_flex_flash_attn_backward` only at the host stage, if not skipped."
msgstr ""
"与前向传播相同，为了形成 `dsink` 计算的完整、无重叠分解，我们可以在 host 阶段（如果未跳过）仅将 `sink` 传入 "
"`_flex_flash_attn_backward` 来计算部分 `dsink`。"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:623
msgid ""
"And according to the formula of <b>dsink computation</b>, `dsink` is "
"required to be sum-reduced along the `seqlen_q` dim, therefore, to get the "
"reduced `dsink` for each cp rank, we have to additionally launch an all-"
"reduce communication with `ReduceOp.Sum`, and wait it to complete before "
"returning from the backward."
msgstr ""
"根据 <b>dsink 计算</b> 的公式，`dsink` 需要沿 `seqlen_q` 维度进行求和归约，因此，为了获得每个 cp rank 的归约"
" `dsink`，我们还需要额外启动一个 `ReduceOp.Sum` 的 all-reduce 通信，并等待其完成后再从反向传播返回。"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:624
msgid ""
"However, the tricky thing is that during the acutal training scenario, the "
"learnable `sink` tensor will be considered as a regular parameter in the "
"model similar to `bias` in `nn.Linear` layer. So under some popular training"
" frameworks, such as `Megatron-LM`, `FSDP`, the sum-reduction across cp "
"ranks of the partial gradients of `sink` might be automatically applied "
"within the whole `dp x cp` mesh."
msgstr ""
"然而，棘手的是，在实际训练场景中，可学习的 `sink` 张量将被视为模型中的常规参数，类似于 `nn.Linear` 层中的 "
"`bias`。因此，在一些流行的训练框架（如 `Megatron-LM`、`FSDP`）下，`sink` 部分梯度跨 cp rank "
"的求和归约可能会在整个 `dp x cp` mesh 中自动应用。"

#: ../../source/blog/attn_sink.md:625
msgid ""
"To avoid repeated reduction, we provide the environment variable "
"`MAGI_ATTENTION_DSINK_ALL_REDUCE_OP` to let the user specify the all-reduce "
"op for `dsink` within MagiAttention (<em>see the [docs](https://sandai-"
"org.github.io/MagiAttention/docs/main/env_variables.html#for-correctness) "
"for more details</em>). Defaults to `none` to <b>NOT</b> apply any reduction"
" to `dsink` and let the framework handle it. Other options include `sum` and"
" `avg` if needed."
msgstr ""
"为避免重复归约，我们提供了环境变量 `MAGI_ATTENTION_DSINK_ALL_REDUCE_OP`，让用户在 MagiAttention "
"中指定 `dsink` 的 all-reduce 操作（<em>详情请参阅[文档](https://sandai-"
"org.github.io/MagiAttention/docs/main/env_variables.html#for-"
"correctness)</em>）。默认为 `none`，即 <b>不</b>对 `dsink` 应用任何归约，由框架处理。如需其他选项，可选 "
"`sum` 和 `avg`。"

